    "preparations_description": "The main herbal preparations of Juniperus communis are juniper berry tea, juniper berry tincture, juniper berry oil, juniper berry infusion, and juniper oil. Juniper berry tea is prepared by infusing the berries in hot water to relieve digestive issues and alleviate symptoms of colds and flu. Juniper berry tincture is a concentrated liquid extract used to treat urinary tract infections and kidney stones due to its diuretic properties. Juniper berry oil is obtained through steam distillation and applied topically to reduce pain and inflammation in the joints. Juniper oil, also obtained through steam distillation, is used in aromatherapy to relieve stress and anxiety due to its calming effects.",
